<p>Dave&#8217;s back from vacation and he and John are back in action answering your questions and solving your problems. But first they talk about today&#8217;s announcement from Apple about their plans for pulling out of future Macworld Expos. &nbsp;This show goes from basic to geeky and back, all while your favorite geeks do their best to ensure you understand each and every bit. Dave&#8217;s still without power, so this one&#8217;s recorded in Pilot Pete&#8217;s basement &#8220;on the road&#8221;-style.  Your geeks are dedicated to getting the show out no matter what!</p>
